  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 1c1edaa2fbe0b554faf52ecc3d47aad9, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  journalFont: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b8a37b71cbd2a284db1c62ce875b70d6, type: 2}
  pageTurnSound: {fileID: 0}
  entry1: 'The island is not done with you. Start at the tower: find the fuel hidden
    there. The boat is broken, and its pieces are scattered around the island. Fuel
    first, then the pieces, then the way out.'
  entry2: I hid the rudder where the trees swallow the light
  entry3: The mast rolled down toward the rocky cliff side
  entry4: The plank is near the old stone ruins, half buried
  entry5: The engine sank into the cursed stones to the north. Solve their pattern
    and it will be yours. No two connected stones can share the same color.
  entry6: The boat is ready. Return with fuel before the storm takes you.
  entry7: The storm is here. Leave now.
